          <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, sizing, spacing, and state mappings that define the Radio Button's visual language.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">The full component set covers Label Position &times; Size &times; State &times; Direction.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Label Position</strong></td><td><code>Left</code> (default), <code>Top</code></td><td>Left = horizontal row (web default). Top = vertical stack for constrained space or long labels.</td></tr>
